en-text=\"Preberi ve\u010d\"><\/span> <\/div> <\/div>  <div data-empty=\"0\" class=\"ti-review-item source-Google ti-image-layout-thumbnail\" data-time=\"\" data-id=\"cfcd208495d565ef66e7dff9f98764da\" data-language=\"\"> <div class=\"ti-inner\"> <div class=\"ti-review-header\"> <div class=\"ti-platform-icon ti-with-tooltip\"> <span class=\"ti-tooltip\">Objavljeno na Google<\/span> <trustindex-image data-imgurl=\"https:\/\/cdn.trustindex.io\/assets\/platform\/Google\/icon.svg\" alt=\"Google\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\"><\/trustindex-image> <\/div> <div class=\"ti-profile-img\"> <trustindex-image data-imgurl=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/ACg8ocKGm1Aa_xqIK_M0DsUdjb8x6iVSrq5AHu7yeQERNgHWBbEoPAPU=w40-h40-c-rp-mo-br100\" alt=\"Tja\u0161a Ro\u017ei\u010d profile picture\" loading=\"lazy\"><\/trustindex-image> <\/div> <div class=\"ti-profile-details\"> <div class=\"ti-name\"> Tja\u0161a Ro\u017ei\u010d <\/div> <div class=\"ti-date\"><\/div> <\/div> <\/div> <span class=\"ti-stars\"><trustindex-image class=\"ti-star\" data-imgurl=\"https:\/\/cdn.trustindex.io\/assets\/platform\/Google\/star\/f.svg\" alt=\"Google star 1\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\"><\/trustindex-image><trustindex-image class=\"ti-star\" data-imgurl=\"https:\/\/cdn.trustindex.io\/assets\/platform\/Google\/star\/f.svg\" alt=\"Google star 2\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\"><\/trustindex-image><trustindex-image class=\"ti-star\" data-imgurl=\"https:\/\/cdn.trustindex.io\/assets\/platform\/Google\/star\/f.svg\" alt=\"Google star 3\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\"><\/trustindex-image><trustindex-image class=\"ti-star\" data-imgurl=\"https:\/\/cdn.trustindex.io\/assets\/platform\/Google\/star\/f.svg\" alt=\"Google star 4\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\"><\/trustindex-image><trustindex-image class=\"ti-star\" data-imgurl=\"https:\/\/cdn.trustindex.io\/assets\/platform\/Google\/star\/f.svg\" alt=\"Google star 5\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\"><\/trustindex-image><span class=\"ti-verified-review ti-verified-platform\"><span class=\"ti-verified-tooltip\">Trustindex preveri, ali je izvorni vir ocene Google.<\/span><\/span><\/span> <div class=\"ti-review-text-container ti-review-content\"><!-- R-CONTENT -->Iskreno \u2014 Rabimbox me je re\u0161il tako elegantno, da se \u0161e danes smejim svoji samozavesti. Bila sem prepri\u010dana, da imam doma ve\u010d kot dovolj svojih \u0161katel za vse stvari. No, potem sem za\u010dela pakirati \u2026 in ugotovila, da sem \u017eivela v iluziji. \ud83d\ude04\n\nRabimbox mi je dostavil njihove izjemno prakti\u010dne boxe, v katere sem kon\u010dno lahko spravila vse, kar sem mislila, da \u201cbo \u017ee \u0161lo\u201d. Najboljsi del? Nobenega lomljenja kartona, nobenega lepljenja, nobenega \u201ckje je spet selotejp?\u201d.\n\nKo pa so bile stvari, ki jih trenutno ne potrebujem, pripravljene za odhod, je ekipa Rabimbox pri\u0161la, boxe prevzela in jih varen odpeljala v skladi\u0161\u010de. Profesionalno, hitro, brez zapletov. Zelo prijazno so mi tudi pojasnili, da ko bom naslednji\u010d potrebovala kaksn box iz skladi\u0161\u010da ali pa potrebovala dodatno shranjevanje, naj jih preprosto poklicem in bodo dobro poskrbeli za moje stvari \ud83d\ude04\n\nTop ekipa, enostaven proces in \u017eelja, da bi jih \u201codkrila\u201d \u017ee prej!\n\nToplo priporo\u010dam Rabimbox vsem, ki se selijo, nimajo dovolj prostora ali pa \u2014 tako kot jaz \u2014 mislijo, da imajo doma dovolj \u0161katel \u2026 dokler ne za\u010dnejo pakirati. \ud83d\ude09<!-- R-CONTENT --><\/div> <span class=\"ti-read-more\" data-container=\".ti-review-content\" data-collapse-text=\"Skrij se\" data-open-text=\"Preberi ve\u010d\"><\/span> <\/div> <\/div>  <\/div> <div class=\"ti-controls-line\"> <div class=\"dot\"><\/div> <\/div> <\/div>   <\/div> <\/div> <\/template><\/pre><div data-src=\"https:\/\/cdn.trustindex.io\/loader.js?wp-widget\" data-template-id=\"trustindex-google-widget-